1199
01:21:32,200 --> 01:21:34,200
[action music]

1200
01:21:44,040 --> 01:21:46,040
[action music continues]

1201
01:21:56,320 --> 01:21:58,320
[action music intensifies]

1202
01:22:02,240 --> 01:22:03,840
King Narai has passed away.

1203
01:22:04,920 --> 01:22:06,920
[tense music]

1204
01:22:07,840 --> 01:22:10,400
