1205
01:22:12,200 --> 01:22:13,800
You killed him!

1206
01:22:14,680 --> 01:22:16,640
-[thwacks]
-[grunts]

1207
01:22:17,280 --> 01:22:21,000
-[thwacking]
-[men grunting]

1208
01:22:25,440 --> 01:22:27,440
[tense music]

1209
01:22:29,640 --> 01:22:30,600
