-[shouts]

1214
01:22:44,680 --> 01:22:45,760
[thuds]

1215
01:22:46,240 --> 01:22:48,240
[ominous music]

1216
01:22:58,040 --> 01:22:59,760
[grunting]

1217
01:23:00,800 --> 01:23:02,520
[spitting]

1218
01:23:03,440 --> 01:23:04,880
Get him up.

1219
01:23:07,680 --> 01:23:09,120
-[thuds]
-Don't stand up!

1220
01:23:12,640 --> 01:23:14,160
You cunning bastard!

1221
01:23:14,880 --> 01:23:16,320
Don't act all innocent.

1222
01:23:17,200 --> 01:23:19,920
Do you remember your letter?

1223
01:23:20,400 --> 01:23:22,400
[percussive music]

1224
01:23:22,960 --> 01:23:25,120
The one that you secretly sent
to your foreign master?

1225
01:23:26,120 --> 01:23:27,640
Do you think we didn't know about that?

1226
01:23:28,000 --> 01:23:29,960
We knew about it!

1227
01:23:39,320 --> 01:23:40,640
Constance.

1228
01:23:41,920 --> 01:23:43,480
You lowlife bastard.

1229
01:23:45,400 --> 01:23:48,120
How dare you try to give away
my land to your people.

1230
01:23:49,640 --> 01:23:52,080
How dare you use Shorty as a puppet

1231
01:23:53,440 --> 01:23:55,320
to rule over the kingdom yourself.

1232
01:23:56,240 --> 01:23:58,320
[Phetracha] How dare you.

1233
01:23:59,040 --> 01:24:03,120
Ayutthaya has given you so much
for over ten years.

1234
01:24:05,680 --> 01:24:07,240
Don't you have any shame?

1235
01:24:08,480 --> 01:24:10,480
[tense music]

1236
01:24:11,560 --> 01:24:13,680
How could you do this to my country?

1237
01:24:14,720 --> 01:24:15,600
How could you?

1238
01:24:17,320 --> 01:24:18,280
How...

1239
01:24:19,800 --> 01:24:21,760
did you know about the letter?

1240
01:24:22,360 --> 01:24:23,680
-[shouts]
-[grunts]

1241
01:24:24,840 --> 01:24:26,840
[tense music]

1242
01:24:28,480 --> 01:24:30,360
[Phetracha] I would know
even if there was no letter.

1243
01:24:30,840 --> 01:24:32,160
It's in your nature

1244
01:24:33,440 --> 01:24:35,320
to be dishonest, deceitful,

1245
01:24:35,560 --> 01:24:37,440
fraudulent, and treacherous.

1246
01:24:40,400 --> 01:24:41,640
You deserve to die.

1247
01:24:41,960 --> 01:24:43,960
[tense music]

1248
01:24:46,760 --> 01:24:49,000
I'll kill you right now.

1249
01:24:49,960 --> 01:24:51,240
-Go to hell!
-Please!

1250
01:24:58,920 --> 01:25:00,800
[whimpers]
Can I see my wife...

1251
01:25:03,360 --> 01:25:05,360
and my children one last time, please?

1252
01:25:05,720 --> 01:25:07,720
[tense music]

1253
01:25:22,360 --> 01:25:24,160
[Dech] He will definitely be executed
anyway.

1254
01:25:31,600 --> 01:25:33,720
Please show him mercy one last time.

1255
01:25:38,400 --> 01:25:39,760
I will take him there.

1256
01:25:40,000 --> 01:25:41,120
I'll go.

1257
01:25:44,520 --> 01:25:46,760
You owe him. I can't trust you.

1258
01:25:49,640 --> 01:25:51,160
You became an ambassador because of him.

1259
01:25:54,040 --> 01:25:55,120
Take him.

1260
01:25:56,120 --> 01:25:58,120
[tense music]

1261
01:26:12,880 --> 01:26:14,400
Don't worry about Lady Mali

1262
01:26:15,240 --> 01:26:16,560
and your son.

1263
01:26:17,200 --> 01:26:18,640
Karaked and I

1264
01:26:19,000 --> 01:26:20,440
will take good care of them.

1265
01:26:21,560 --> 01:26:23,560
[dramatic music]

1266
01:26:30,960 --> 01:26:32,960
[dramatic music continues]

1267
01:26:33,720 --> 01:26:34,800
Lord Rueang.

1268
01:26:35,320 --> 01:26:36,960
[Phaulkon whimpers]

1269
01:26:37,680 --> 01:26:39,680
[somber music]

1270
01:27:13,320 --> 01:27:15,320
[somber music continues]

1271
01:27:26,480 --> 01:27:28,480
[dramatic music]

1272
01:27:30,360 --> 01:27:33,080
[chains jangling]

1273
01:27:43,200 --> 01:27:44,600
Tong Guyomar.

1274
01:27:46,120 --> 01:27:48,120
[dramatic music]

1275
01:27:52,720 --> 01:27:53,920
I'm sorry.

1276
01:27:54,320 --> 01:27:57,280
[sobbing]

1277
01:28:00,440 --> 01:28:02,440
I've warned you.

1278
01:28:05,440 --> 01:28:07,960
I told you, haven't I?

1279
01:28:10,120 --> 01:28:12,240
You have brought great shame

1280
01:28:13,560 --> 01:28:16,440
upon me and our children.

1281
01:28:18,480 --> 01:28:20,480
[dramatic music]

1282
01:28:22,080 --> 01:28:23,400
[sobbing]

1283
01:28:25,280 --> 01:28:26,560
It's all my fault.

1284
01:28:28,280 --> 01:28:30,520
[both sobbing]

1285
01:28:37,520 --> 01:28:39,520
[dramatic music]

1286
01:28:43,960 --> 01:28:46,640
[Mali sobbing]

1287
01:28:49,080 --> 01:28:50,840
Does it hurt?

1288
01:28:53,320 --> 01:28:54,920
Why did they have to beat you up so badly

1289
01:28:56,120 --> 01:28:58,400
