1290
01:29:01,040 --> 01:29:02,200
It doesn't hurt.

1291
01:29:05,560 --> 01:29:06,920
King Narai has passed away.

1292
01:29:11,520 --> 01:29:12,800
[Phaulkon] I don't feel any pain.

1293
01:29:14,960 --> 01:29:16,560
I don't feel any pain at all.

1294
01:29:20,040 --> 01:29:20,960
You...

1295
01:29:21,760 --> 01:29:23,720
What's going to happen to you?

1296
01:29:28,440 --> 01:29:29,880
I'm here to say goodbye.

1297
01:29:30,280 --> 01:29:32,280
[dramatic music]

1298
01:29:36,840 --> 01:29:39,120
Earl Wisarn Sunthorn

1299
01:29:41,160 --> 01:29:42,600
promised me

1300
01:29:44,640 --> 01:29:46,200
that he and his wife

1301
01:29:47,800 --> 01:29:50,400
will take care of you
and our children for me.

1302
01:29:51,240 --> 01:29:52,920
So, I'm not worrying that much

1303
01:29:54,040 --> 01:29:56,520
even if I have to die today.

1304
01:30:00,840 --> 01:30:02,320
Can I just...

1305
01:30:07,960 --> 01:30:11,080
see my children one last time, please?

1306
01:30:12,840 --> 01:30:13,960
No, you can't.

1307
01:30:14,640 --> 01:30:15,920
[sobbing]
Tong Guyomar.

1308
01:30:16,880 --> 01:30:18,880
[dramatic music]

1309
01:30:20,440 --> 01:30:22,040
I'm sorry.

1310
01:30:23,600 --> 01:30:25,600
I know I did terrible things

1311
01:30:26,600 --> 01:30:28,040
to you

1312
01:30:29,280 --> 01:30:30,640
and to our children.

1313
01:30:35,200 --> 01:30:39,880
Please, let me see them
one last time before I die.

1314
01:30:40,760 --> 01:30:42,600
I'm begging you.

1315
01:30:43,120 --> 01:30:47,040
[both sobbing]

1316
01:30:48,600 --> 01:30:50,440
I really can't let that happen.

1317
01:30:51,720 --> 01:30:53,720
[dramatic music]

1318
01:30:55,400 --> 01:30:57,440
-[whimpers]
-[Mali sobbing]

1319
01:31:02,120 --> 01:31:03,720
Our two children

1320
01:31:06,240 --> 01:31:07,640
should remember

1321
01:31:08,280 --> 01:31:09,280
their father

1322
01:31:10,440 --> 01:31:12,120
as a man of dignity

1323
01:31:15,440 --> 01:31:16,840
and greatness.

1324
01:31:18,840 --> 01:31:21,000
A well-respected man.

1325
01:31:24,960 --> 01:31:25,920
They should not

1326
01:31:27,360 --> 01:31:28,320
see their father

1327
01:31:29,440 --> 01:31:30,960
as a man who is chained,

1328
01:31:31,920 --> 01:31:33,240
hurt,

1329
01:31:34,840 --> 01:31:37,440
and stripped of his dignity.

1330
01:31:40,800 --> 01:31:41,920
Please.

1331
01:31:42,960 --> 01:31:43,920
Tong Guyomar.

1332
01:31:44,680 --> 01:31:46,160
Please.

1333
01:31:49,720 --> 01:31:51,720
[dramatic music]

1334
01:31:53,800 --> 01:31:55,040
[Mali] Jorge and JoÃ£o

1335
01:31:56,360 --> 01:31:58,120
will come

1336
01:31:58,480 --> 01:32:00,320
to say goodnight soon.

1337
01:32:01,920 --> 01:32:03,280
[whimpers]

1338
01:32:04,080 --> 01:32:05,880
You should go.

1339
01:32:06,240 --> 01:32:08,240
[somber music]

1340
01:32:24,880 --> 01:32:26,880
[somber music continues]

1341
01:32:38,960 --> 01:32:40,560
[pants]

